        Constructs a new RSA-ECDSA EncrypterManager.

        Please note that the InputStream senderSigningKey will not be closed.

        Parameters:
        senderSigningKey - the serialized Tink signing key.
        Throws:
        java.security.GeneralSecurityException - if the initialization fails.
        java.io.IOException - if the given sender signing key cannot be read.
